        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Neuromyelitis Optica Spectrum Disorder Consortium Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the National Institutes of Health to establish a national consortium to coordinate and support research on neuromyelitis optica spectrum disorder, including by awarding grants. This is a neurological disease that can cause blindness, paralysis, and premature death.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
